From 6da4ce734354bc21ea5cdcae7c8a9b92163dc473 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ci7lus <7887955+ci7lus@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:52:28 +0900
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add callback for arib bml

fix: Fix BML section callback - ensure transport/sections_proc on active stream, add diagnostics

fix: BML - use UNKNOWN_ES to prevent decoder, force FLAG_FILTERED via SetPIDFilter

debug: BML - add more diagnostics and fix sections loop bug

fix: BML - remove accidental packet drop in demux loop, use SPU_ES to see if it fixes filtering
---
